label: Print 1
description:
Two designs. Design 1: Text that says "I CAME/I SAW/I CAME AGAIN. VALENTINE'S DAY PCP 1999."
Design 2: two mostly nude figures, one AMAB and the other AFAB. The AFAB figure, which kneels on the ground pulling fabric off of the AMAB figure, says, "This time I get to be emperor!"
